This code allows you to have one buffer per channel in ZenIRC.
I use it together with MTraceMode to make it possible to follow the activity going on in the different buffers.  -- MicheleBini

Download:

* Lisp:zenirc-chanbuf.el

Usage -- Put the following in your .emacs to enable zenirc-chanbuf and have it autoloaded with zenirc.

    (eval-after-load "zenirc"
       '(progn
           (load "/path/to/zenirc-chanbuf.el")
           (add-hook 'zenirc-mode-hook  'zenirc-chanbuf-minor-mode)))

----

ZenIRC
